text:
Dear Gura, 

Happy Birthday! 
Thank you for many years of laughter and smiles. And thank you for a lot more than that. This might be too personal to share on here, but it is why I am so happy for you to be my kami oshi. You did more for me than any other vtuber by far.
 I never meant to bring negativity to you, its neither of our faults. Gura, I never want you to hate me. I always want your heart, your love, and all of your cuteness. Your cuteness has no limits, from "blonde" to "white". I ask too much of you all the time, as I can't do anything for you. Yet, shorkie keeps on giving.
Your eyes and influence are everywhere in this "world", and thank you for that. I am happy how well "Myth" took care of you, and treated me like family.

Really thank you. I hope you are able to continue what you love as long as you live. If I do ever get a shark encounter, in my lifetime, I do not mind paying for bait and livestock.

Happy Birthday, Gura
Chumbud
